## Formatting Rules

- Capture all four dimensions before recommending.
- Always shortlist 1-2 patterns with rationale per dimension.
- Tradeoffs cite the source (Engelbart, Suchman, Shneiderman, Bansal).
- Prompt scaffolds are concrete, not abstract.
- Evolution plan is optional, but offer it explicitly.
